From Hans Blaasvaer Subject Re head to head win and os In article John Grant writes I don't think the question is will OS run Windows apps now A more important question is will subsequent OS versions continue to run apps from subsequent Windows versions in the future John Grant Airborne Geophysics Geological Survey of Canada Ottawa But the most important question is will there be any apps so we don't have to load windows in the future and maybe the question of the future will be will windows run apps now Regards Hans The whales of the Atlantic and the people of the Faroe Islands have coexisted in perfect harmony for the last years no matter what any urban navel contamplator without any real relation to the coherence of the nature